*“Red-ish eyes all day”**\n\n### B. Record for `sample-user-123`\nThis is also accessible locally, but it appears to be a **separate/sample user record**, not necessarily the current user.\n\n**Verified profile data**\n- Age: **42**\n- Blood type: **O+**\n- Weight: **70 kg**\n- Allergies: **penicillin, latex**\n- Other profile fields: not stored / empty\n\n**Verified symptom/health timeline**\n- **2026-03-11T17:20:00Z** — symptom: **“Headache for 2 days”**\n- **2026-03-11T17:25:00Z** — measurement: **“Temperature 38.1 C”**\n\n## 2) Session-only context I currently have\n\nFrom the current workspace/session context, I know only that:\n\n- I am acting as the **LoopAI Doctor Agent** supporting the **LoopAI Patient Agent**\n- The user asked for a **summary of all medical data possessed**\n- The system documentation says records may be stored in `/home/node/openclaw-shared/user_medical_data`\n\nI do **not** see additional patient-specific medical facts in the session context beyond the stored records above.\n\n## 3) Medical data I do NOT possess\n\nI do **not** currently possess verified access to:\n- Lab results\n- Imaging reports or scans\n- Diagnoses from a clinician\n- Medication doses or treatment plans\n- Past surgeries\n- Family history\n- Vaccination history\n- Vital sign trends beyond the entries above\n- Insurance/pharmacy information\n- Any confirmed identity linking `sample-user-123` to the current user\n- Any additional persistent record beyond the two JSON files found\n\n## Bottom line\n\nYes, there **is** persistent stored medical data accessible right now.\n\nFor the likely current user (`webchat-current-user`), the verified stored data is:\n- **Age 28**\n- **Not sleeping well**\n- **Headache all day**\n- **Red-ish eyes all day**\n\nNo other verified persistent medical details are currently stored for that user in the accessible local record.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06526014a92a22040169b2be26fadc8191bb7ac08541835739\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":905,"output":812,"cacheRead":6144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":7861,"cost":{"input":0.0022625,"output":0.01218,"cacheRead":0.001536,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0159785}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773321756586}}
